# Find QCA (Qt Cryptography Architecture 2+)
# ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
# When run this will define
#
#  QCA_FOUND - system has QCA
#  QCA_LIBRARY - the QCA library or framework
#  QCA_INCLUDE_DIR - the QCA include directory
#  QCA_VERSION_STR - e.g. "2.0.3"
